00:32:38.960 --> 00:32:43.750
it mean to the enterprise? And I said, "Okay,
let me use a collaboration platform to ask

00:32:43.750 --> 00:32:46.500
that question.”
I asked people, "What are your five predictions

00:32:46.500 --> 00:32:50.930
for the future of collaboration?”
I got a ton of input from people everywhere.

00:32:50.930 --> 00:32:55.400
I mean, people in the industry, out of the
industry, analysts, you know, just people

00:32:55.400 --> 00:33:00.220
that are users of the technology.
And I gathered all that input, and I think

00:33:00.220 --> 00:33:04.190
this is a room for an ap on -- somebody has
to create for Twitter, if somehow you can

00:33:04.190 --> 00:33:08.500
get -- today it's manually, you know, I gathered
all the information, and I had one of our

