00:45:39.730 --> 00:45:43.130
I discovered there were five women in a class
of 250.

00:45:43.130 --> 00:45:46.260
And I told this story.
I called my dad the next day, and said "I

00:45:46.260 --> 00:45:49.130
want to come home." And he said, "It's too
late.

00:45:49.130 --> 00:45:52.269
You decided to go there.
Now, you stay there.”

00:45:52.269 --> 00:45:56.579
And I thought he was like the meanest dad
in the whole world back then.

00:45:56.579 --> 00:46:00.839
I thought I was very clever, and I knew how
to get around this problem.

00:46:00.839 --> 00:46:04.730
So I called my mom.
