00:46:04.730 --> 00:46:08.690
her cooking.
Now, I have a teenager now, and I know if

00:46:08.690 --> 00:46:13.299
he called me and said he was missing my cooking,
I would have him home on the next flight.

00:46:13.299 --> 00:46:18.820
But my mom had more sense than that, I think.
She said, "You stay in school; I'll send you

00:46:18.820 --> 00:46:20.819
food.”
And so, I ended up finishing my engineering

00:46:20.819 --> 00:46:23.130
school.
