00:46:38.150 --> 00:46:42.020
engineering at Cornell, and I started in the
semiconductor industry as an engineer -- as

00:46:42.020 --> 00:46:48.289
a line engineer actually -- and then, worked
up to become the CTO for Motorolla, semiconductor

00:46:48.289 --> 00:46:50.900
business.
