00:46:50.900 --> 00:46:55.079
which had no technology.
It was all operations, managing supply chain

00:46:55.079 --> 00:46:58.970
costs, and taking beatings from customers
every other day, because shipments didn't

00:46:58.970 --> 00:47:01.599
happen or something.
