through your career opportunities and your

00:47:07.260 --> 00:47:13.460
growth opportunities as a leader or personal
growth, I think it's to make those transitions

00:47:13.460 --> 00:47:17.990
and use those transitions as opportunities
where you can derive a lot of growth.

00:47:17.990 --> 00:47:22.259
And that can happen in a small company, big
company, personal life, you know, where you

00:47:22.259 --> 00:47:25.090
go through a lot of growth when change happens
in your life.

00:47:25.090 --> 00:47:35.140
So, how do you take all of that which defines
you, who you are as a leader and as a person.

